replies.body:
There are some good steps in here that can definitely help in some circumstances, except the suggestion to log into a friend's account. I definitely **don't** recommend account sharing, as it's bad for security and against the [terms of use](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/legal/termsofuse). 

Good on ya for posting this up though!

